OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FCCTV images show convicted rapist John
OL,8,FAshby on a bus, before following his
OL,9,Fvictim to her home in Walsall before
OL,10,Fthe attack.
OL,12,FWarning: This article contains
OL,13,Fexpletives and details of a
OL,14,Fdistressing nature
OL,16,FA man has been jailed for life after
OL,17,Fpleading guilty to the religiously-
OL,18,Faggravated rape and assault of a Sikh
OL,19,Fwoman in Walsall, who he wrongly
OL,20,Fbelieved to be Muslim.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FJohn Ashby, who's 32 and of no fixed
OL,8,Fabode, attacked the victim after
OL,9,Fspotting her travelling on the bus. He
OL,10,Ffollowed her home and entered while
OL,11,Fshe was upstairs.
OL,13,FCCTV footage from 25 October 2025
OL,14,Fshowed Ashby getting off the same bus
OL,15,Fas the woman.
OL,17,FHe followed her for around ten
OL,18,Fminutes, with some distance between
OL,19,Fthem. She did not know she was being
OL,20,Ffollowed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FHe was then seen loitering outside her
OL,8,Fhouse, where he found a stick around a
OL,9,Fmetre and a half long, which he hid
OL,10,Finside his clothes.
OL,12,FCCTV then picked up a scream from
OL,13,Finside the woman's house.
OL,15,FExtracts from body-worn police footage
OL,16,Fshowing the woman, who cannot be
OL,17,Fidentified, were played to a jury of
OL,18,Fsix men and six women.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FThe footage showed the woman being
OL,8,Fcomforted by a female officer. She
OL,9,Fsaid her attacker had called her a
OL,10,F"bloody Muslim bitch".
OL,12,F'British master'
OL,14,FThe woman, said by witnesses to have
OL,15,Fbeen hysterical while repeatedly
OL,16,Fscreaming, told police she had been
OL,17,Fraped in a bathroom by the intruder,
OL,18,Fwho was armed with a stick he found
OL,19,Foutside, and claimed to be a "British
OL,20,Fmaster".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@UO]{D@^OU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FIn a video interview played during
OL,8,FAshby's trial, the victim told police:
OL,9,F"He had a stick in his hand. I said
OL,10,F'who are you' and I started screaming.
OL,12,F"He switched off the light. He said 'I
OL,13,Fjust want fun with you'. He said 'you
OL,14,Fare a f****** Muslim bitch'.
OL,16,F"I said I am not a Muslim, I am a
OL,17,FSikh."
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FThe woman also told police the man was
OL,8,Finitially aggressive and had
OL,9,Fcontinuously verbally abusing her, but
OL,10,Fthen became calm.
OL,12,FAs the video interview was being
OL,13,Fplayed to the jury, Ashby was thought
OL,14,Fto have muttered something under his
OL,15,Fbreath.
OL,17,FA member of the public then left the
OL,18,Fpublic gallery and approached the
OL,19,Fglass-fronted dock and swore at Ashby.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FAshby responded by telling the man to
OL,8,F"get the f*** out of my face" and also
OL,9,Fshouted at another member of the
OL,10,Fpublic who had remained seated in the
OL,11,Fpublic gallery.
OL,13,FThe defendant then refused to return
OL,14,Fto the trial for some time, until he
OL,15,Freturned and changed all his pleas to
OL,16,Fguilty.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
