OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FAshby admitted rape, intentional
OL,8,Fstrangulation, robbery as he stole
OL,9,Fjewellery and a mobile phone as he
OL,10,Fleft the house, and racially-
OL,11,Faggravated assault.
OL,13,F'Deeply unpleasant, racist and
OL,14,FIslamophobic'
OL,16,FDefending Ashby, Ms Michelle Heeley KC
OL,17,Fsaid: "He is someone who does have
OL,18,Fmental health difficulties."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FShe added that he was living on the
OL,8,Fstreets and had taken drugs because of
OL,9,Fhis mental health difficulties. She
OL,10,Falso said he had been diagnosed with
OL,11,Fautism and Asperger syndrome.
OL,13,FDuring the sentencing at Birmingham
OL,14,FCrown Court today, Judge Mr Justice
OL,15,FPepperall told Ashby: "You armed
OL,16,Fyourself with a big stick. You ignored
OL,17,Fher screams.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,F"These offences have had a devastating
OL,8,Fimapct on this woman. She and her
OL,9,Fpartner could not bring themselves to
OL,10,Fspend another night in their home.
OL,12,F"Six months on, the woman and partner
OL,13,Fhave described the profund effect of
OL,14,Fthese crimes on every aspcect of her
OL,15,Flife."
OL,17,FHe continued: "It has meant she is
OL,18,Falways on edge. She lives in a state
OL,19,Fof fear. When home alone she locks
OL,20,Fherself in her room.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,F"She experiences flashbacks and
OL,8,Fcontinually replays what happened in
OL,9,Fher mind. She suffers panic attacks
OL,10,Fthat on occasion have meant she had to
OL,11,Fgo to hospital.
OL,13,F"She can no longer work."
OL,15,FThe judge told Ashby: "You had
OL,16,Fhostility against this woman because
OL,17,Fshe is Asian and because you thought
OL,18,Fshe was Muslim."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
