OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777119066
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life for racist
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FHe described Ashby as "deeply
OL,8,Funpleasant, racist and an Islamophobe"
OL,9,Fand says there was some planning
OL,10,Finvolved in his offending as he
OL,11,F"picked her out on the bus" and
OL,12,Ffollowed her home.
OL,14,FHe continued: "Your victim has waited
OL,15,Fmonths and prepared for trial. Your
OL,16,Flate guilty plea did not spare her."
OL,18,FAshby has been sentenced to life in
OL,19,Fprison with a minimum of 14 years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
